---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Driving Efficiency Forward: Spotlight on F&S Expedited LLC | Community Spotlight"
  description="Learn about F&S Expedited LLC, a reliable, fast, and customer-focused logistics partner based in Shelby, NC."
>
  <article class="pt-32 pb-24 px-4 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-16 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-orange-500/20 bg-orange-500/5">
          <span class="text-orange-500 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Community Spotlight</span>
          <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-orange-500/30"></span>
          <span class="text-brand-sky/60 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest">Vol #1 Article #5 • March 2026</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-8 tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
          Driving Efficiency Forward: <br />
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-red-500">Spotlight on F&S Expedited LLC</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-sky/80 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto italic">
          Reliable, Fast, and Customer-Focused Logistics from Shelby, NC
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Main Image Placeholder -->
      <div class="aspect-video bg-brand-dark border border-white/5 rounded-3xl mb-16 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500/20 to-transparent opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-center">
           <span class="text-brand-sky/20 font-heading text-4xl font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] transform -rotate-12 px-4">Shelby Web Company <br/> Community Spotlight</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-sky/90 mb-12">
          Featured on <a href="/" class="text-brand-cyan hover:underline decoration-brand-cyan/30 underline-offset-4">Shelby Web Company</a> | Spotlighting <strong>F&S Expedited LLC</strong>
        </p>

        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          In today's fast-paced logistics landscape, businesses need more than just transportation—they need reliability, speed, and a partner they can trust. That's exactly what <strong>F&S Expedited LLC</strong> brings to the table.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-orange-500">01.</span> Who Is F&S Expedited LLC?
        </h2>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5">
            <ul class="space-y-4 list-none p-0 m-0">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-orange-500 font-bold">📍</span>
                <span class="text-brand-sky/80"><strong>Location:</strong> Shelby, North Carolina</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-orange-500 font-bold">🚛</span>
                <span class="text-brand-sky/80"><strong>Type:</strong> Interstate Freight Carrier</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-orange-500 font-bold">🌎</span>
                <span class="text-brand-sky/80"><strong>Coverage:</strong> United States</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-orange-500 font-bold">👤</span>
                <span class="text-brand-sky/80"><strong>Owner:</strong> Joe Aldrich</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed self-center">
            F&S Expedited LLC is an active interstate freight carrier based in Shelby, North Carolina, providing transportation services across the United States. Their operation focuses on timely deliveries and maintaining high service standards.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-orange-500">02.</span> Services That Keep Your Business Moving
        </h2>
        
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-orange-500/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Expedited Freight</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">Specializing in shipments where time is critical, prioritizing urgent deliveries without sacrificing safety.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-orange-500/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Trucking & Transport</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">Moving goods securely across regional and interstate routes, ensuring on-time and intact arrivals.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-orange-500/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Time-Sensitive Delivery</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">Valuable handling for industries where delays are costly, providing dependable turnaround times.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-orange-500/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Logistics Support</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">Helping optimize delivery routes and improve overall supply chain efficiency through coordinated support.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500/10 to-transparent border border-orange-500/20 p-8 my-12 rounded-3xl">
          <p class="text-white font-medium italic mb-6">"We're proud to partner with Joe Aldrich and F&S Expedited LLC. Their dedication to quality logistics mirrors our own commitment to excellence for local businesses in Shelby and beyond."</p>
          <p class="text-orange-500 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">— Shelby Web Company Editor's Note</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-orange-500">03.</span> Why Choose F&S Expedited LLC?
        </h2>
        <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 list-none p-0 mb-16">
          <li class="bg-brand-dark/30 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-orange-500">✦</span> <span class="text-brand-sky/80"><strong>Consistency:</strong> On time, every time</span>
          </li>
          <li class="bg-brand-dark/30 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-orange-500">✦</span> <span class="text-brand-sky/80"><strong>Efficiency:</strong> Streamlined operations</span>
          </li>
          <li class="bg-brand-dark/30 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-orange-500">✦</span> <span class="text-brand-sky/80"><strong>Customer Focus:</strong> Tailored solutions</span>
          </li>
          <li class="bg-brand-dark/30 p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-orange-500">✦</span> <span class="text-brand-sky/80"><strong>Reliability:</strong> A dependable long-term partner</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <!-- Spotlight CTA Section -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-600 to-brand-darkest p-12 rounded-[2rem] text-center relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_50%,rgba(255,165,0,0.1),transparent_70%)]"></div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6 relative z-10 text-center">Meet Your Next Logistics Partner</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-10 relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Looking for a reliable logistics partner? Contact Joe and the F&S Expedited team today.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center relative z-10">
            <a href="https://www.fs-expeditedllc.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-white text-orange-600 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-orange-50 transition-all">
              Visit Website
            </a>
            <a href="tel:7047518141" class="bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-md text-white border border-white/20 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-black/30 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
              Contact Luke
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-24 p-8 bg-brand-dark/50 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl">
          <p class="text-brand-sky/60 text-sm mb-0">
            This article was written and published by <strong>Shelby Web Company</strong> as part of an ongoing series spotlighting local businesses. To learn more about our web design and digital marketing services, visit <a href="/" class="text-brand-cyan hover:underline">www.shelbywebco.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer navigation -->
      <footer class="mt-24 pt-12 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-wrap gap-8 items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
          Back to Blog
        </a>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <a href="/" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a>
          <a href="/about" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">About Us</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
